ANIMATE DEAD

Useage      : cast 'animate dead' <target>
Accumulative: No.
Duration    : Instantaneous.

  creates a zombie servant who will obey your commands.  It has 
  your level d8 hit points, hits as a 2 HD monster, and is
  immune to piercing weapons.  Cityguards and vampire bats hate 
  zombies, and attack them immediately.

Related Topics: SPELL INFO
